description.en:
WarLordToken was born as the manifestation of our Lord's serious thinking about contributing to the futuristic and innovative DeFi ecosystem. Therefore, for the past several days, our Lord has gathered Alchemist and Engineer from around the Realm and building someplace for Peebles who wants to become stronger than before.

Our WarLordToken investors are able to gain more tokens through games and multiply it through stake. However, loss can possibly to happen sometimes since the ARENA is a place for the battle coming after.

How It Works
We also provides the best gaming experience of staking. The specific overview of the staking system is available on our official WarLordToken Medium. Our Lord really loves to write. All of the marvelous writings are written by our respected Lord of WarLordToken.

By utilizing an open source or an open advancement process and is authorized to work in the source code, decentralized software hosted on the Ethereum blockchain in the form of smart contracts (our Lord likes to call it "Tome of Life") presents our users the best trading and staking experiences with the very unique concept of gaming atmosphere.

Therefore, we verily suggest you to visit our Medium to go deep dive into our innovative staking system. You will be very knowledgeable about ARENA and all the terms along the way.
